Step 4 - Verify Documents

API

POST /kyc/verify/{userId}

Flow

Auth Service User
      ↓
Compare User vs PAN
      ↓
Compare User vs Aadhaar
      ↓
Compare PAN vs Aadhaar

Checks

Name Similarity
DOB Match
Success Case
panSimilarity >= 90

aadhaarSimilarity >= 90

documentSimilarity >= 90

all DOB matched

Status

DOCUMENT_VERIFIED

Response

{
   "finalStatus":"DOCUMENT_VERIFIED"
}
Review Case
75-89 similarity

Status

UNDER_REVIEW
Failure Case
Below threshold

Status

REJECTED

